messages.title: YOUR CHOICE AT THIS ELECTION
messages.content: A STRONG, STABLE NATIONAL INTEREST WITH THERESA MAY OR A COALITION OF CHAOS WITH JEREMY CORBYN

images.caption: Steve Baker with Theresa May in the background on one side, and on the other side references to Jeremy Corbyn, Nicola Sturgeon, Tim Farron, and Caroline Lucas.

leaflet.additionalNotes: The leaflet emphasizes a choice between Theresa May's leadership for a stable national interest versus a coalition led by Jeremy Corbyn which is labelled as chaos.
